#: ../../deployment/onnx.rst:3 67e160d590c74147a25f9738b06c5877
msgid "VoxCPM-ONNX"
msgstr "VoxCPM-ONNX"

#: ../../deployment/onnx.rst:5 3e735a0fb07b455289d3677ddbdf90bf
msgid ""
"VoxCPM-ONNX provides ONNX export and ONNX Runtime inference for VoxCPM, "
"with an optional FastAPI REST server."
msgstr ""
"VoxCPM-ONNX 为 VoxCPM 提供 ONNX 导出与 ONNX Runtime 推理，并可选配 FastAPI REST 服务。"

#: ../../deployment/onnx.rst:7 87817ad2c89d4113824baa2645529dad
msgid "Repo: `bluryar/VoxCPM-ONNX <https://github.com/bluryar/VoxCPM-ONNX>`_"
msgstr "仓库：`bluryar/VoxCPM-ONNX <https://github.com/bluryar/VoxCPM-ONNX>`_"

#: ../../deployment/onnx.rst:10 5782a36bced84813bc376f5258a8031b
msgid ""
"This project is **archived** by the author. For active development, "
"consider `VoxCPM.cpp <https://github.com/bluryar/VoxCPM.cpp>`_ instead. "
"The code and documentation were largely AI-generated; use as a reference."
msgstr ""
"作者已将本项目 **归档**。若需要活跃维护的实现，可考虑改用 "
"`VoxCPM.cpp <https://github.com/bluryar/VoxCPM.cpp>`_。"
"代码与文档多为 AI 生成，仅作参考。"

#: ../../deployment/onnx.rst:13 8a41b5c1a03f4a3f8df81e191dbaf1f4
msgid ""
"It provides ONNX export scripts, an ONNX Runtime inference pipeline, and "
"a FastAPI server with an OpenAI-style TTS API."
msgstr ""
"提供 ONNX 导出脚本、ONNX Runtime 推理流水线，以及带 OpenAI 风格 TTS API 的 FastAPI 服务。"

